{"tid":2146803,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【東體爭議】阿特蘭大令意甲嘥1個歐聯位","createTime":"2020-08-08T21:07:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T12:34:14.000Z","uid":78243,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3daf9c361a2c0fd879925bc37f11437f2636b60e","tid":2146803,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T21:07:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YuXr0qj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYuXr0qj.jpg&h=2901618f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3場歐聯分組賽輸晒、入2球、失11球，唔講仲以為係1支三四線聯賽嘅球隊成績，但呢個成績屬於意甲代表阿特蘭大。<br />\n<br />\n阿特蘭大上季意甲爆冷獲得第3位，但其實只係比2支傳統勁旅AC米蘭、羅馬，分別多1分及3分。無可否認，阿特蘭大歷史性獲得歐聯入場券，對細球會係一種鼓舞，但卻意味意甲「放棄」1個歐聯席位，因為阿特蘭大嘅人腳同歐洲賽經驗，都不足以應付呢項大賽，預咗要交學費。<br />\n<br />\n不過，最離譜係阿特蘭大抽到1支唔錯嘅籤，同組最強只有曼城，另外2隊薩格勒布戴拿模、薩克達唔會高得過阿特蘭大幾多，但結果係阿特蘭大竟然吞薩格勒布戴拿模4蛋，主場先入波卻被薩克達絕殺，至於大敗畀曼城，都無謂多講。更令人可怕係，阿特蘭大最終可能6場都輸晒。<br />\n<br />\n2006年因為意甲假波案，令到基爾禾獲益，有得以第4位踢歐聯，但外圍賽被索菲亞利夫斯基淘汰。阿特蘭大比較好彩，可以直入分組賽，但結果都係出醜，最令人遺憾係堂堂意甲季軍，去到歐聯只係最差球隊。"},{"pid":"40792bef52e51e914fa1d8addcd60a1148fc96e4","tid":2146803,"uid":204126,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T21:10:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f94412d515f0fc9064ea3cb50fa13cc15d355d69","tid":2146803,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40792bef52e51e914fa1d8addcd60a1148fc96e4","tid":2146803,"uid":204126,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T21:10:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T21:11:22.000Z","msg":"個意大利人廣東話都幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4c2a3f14d8b1f1deef101384767c3e291c11d43","tid":2146803,"uid":90515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T21:15:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30be34a01091bf38b2351206d88b2f98c05903e9","tid":2146803,"uid":155936,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T21:17:28.000Z","msg":"最後亞特蘭大行得最遠"},{"pid":"ebf8263d5ab817da8469b80c107ad72c972fe2ac","tid":2146803,"uid":78243,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"30be34a01091bf38b2351206d88b2f98c05903e9","tid":2146803,"uid":155936,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T21:17:28.000Z","msg":"最後亞特蘭大行得最遠"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T21:18:22.000Z","msg":"俾白粉報燈到拎埋冠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02ef7a5d3cfd7d305052eb4f4e96990ea7690716","tid":2146803,"uid":222787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T21:30:33.000Z","msg":"一定累佢輸好多啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd77b005ddda9ca022adaa3b323c2289e34689ad","tid":2146803,"uid":34899,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"40792bef52e51e914fa1d8addcd60a1148fc96e4","tid":2146803,"uid":204126,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T21:10:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T04:42:11.000Z","msg":"其實比薩格勒布贏4球真係奇恥大辱黎<br />\n薩格勒布過去19場歐聯贏得一場<br />\n就係贏阿狗1粒"},{"pid":"dc42b3741726f6432c33e6bd72fa1a8eecd77d54","tid":2146803,"uid":52006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T06:08:54.000Z","msg":"8強唯一一隊意甲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6b77749a2a6944fa332ca17f220dc4878bea794","tid":2146803,"uid":185492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T06:16:18.000Z","msg":"等睇拎冠軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2e86235d1c2fb21dde7e319c968abe4980a4d80","tid":2146803,"uid":189068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T09:09:40.000Z","msg":"專登SEARCH返阿特蘭大<br />\n睇下有無人提返依段新聞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c64c465e793f7cc863211a3c5dd9232fc4b3b80c","tid":2146803,"uid":75028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40792bef52e51e914fa1d8addcd60a1148fc96e4","tid":2146803,"uid":20412